<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>٢٥١ - ويأتهم ذكّر <span class="c2">(ر)</span> ضى <span class="c2">(خ)</span> ذ <span class="c2">(ج)</span> نى ونو ... ن تحصنكم <span class="c2">(د)</span> ارك وأنّث <span class="c2">(إ)</span> ذا تلا<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
